Over the weekend, the daughter of a popular CS Eva Kaimenyi used armed policemen to terrorise a family that was having a get-together in the same estate she lives in. A family member said Eva was not for the idea of them throwing a party, and she called in armed policemen, who threw teargas canisters in the house, injuring a pregnant woman and children.The story has gone viral, and reactions include:Yakubu: Very bad. The CS daughter should face the music.Peter: Impunity and gross abuse of office/ power.Brian: May thunder strike them. Poleni!Joyce: Shame on her